rdPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/03/02/privacy-updates-in-5-4/embed/#?secret=dAZ0ZV3kAT\" data-secret=\"dAZ0ZV3kAT\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Changements concernant lâ€™API REST</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sur les <a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;component=REST+API&amp;milestone=5.4&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=status&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;col=focuses&amp;col=keywords&amp;order=priority\">22 modifications</a>&nbsp;liÃ©es Ã  l&rsquo;API REST, les points suivants sont particuliÃ¨rement importants&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WordPress 5.4 prend maintenant en charge la valeur <code>OR</code> du paramÃ¨tre <code>relation</code> des requÃªtes de taxonomies</li><li>Ajout de l&#8217;embarquement (embed) sÃ©lectif de liens</li><li>Modifications de la mÃ©thode <code style=\"font-size: 16px\">WP_REST_Server</code></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Les modifications importantes de l&rsquo;API REST sont listÃ©es dans cet article&nbsp;:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"MhTK4AOGpc\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/02/29/rest-api-changes-in-5-4/\">REST API Changes in 5.4</a></blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;REST API Changes in 5.4&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/02/29/rest-api-changes-in-5-4/embed/#?secret=MhTK4AOGpc\" data-secret=\"MhTK4AOGpc\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth